solution:
Let $C$ be the point where line segment $\overline{OT}$ intersects the circle.

[asy]
unitsize(1.2cm);
defaultpen(linewidth(.7pt)+fontsize(8pt));
dotfactor=3;
pair A=(0,0), B=(-1,0), T=(2,0), C=(1,0);
pair T0=T+10*dir(162);
